page.title: 14LIVING IN A l7th C.HOUSE 3
page.content: BEDROOMS-fitted carpets,colour co-ordinated wallpaper and curtains. Polyester fabric duvets and fitted bottom sheets, foam mattresses on beds GARDEN-Patio area for seats, crazy- paved with stone step.Garden 5Oyds x lOyds on 3 levels.Mostly lawn with flower beds,vegetable patch covering about l/4 of garden area.Fruit bushes and fruit trees.Bounded on two sides by the original high stone wall. GARAGE-In next street,(l6th cent.houses didn't have garage space!)used for family Volkswagon Golf car. Dad's Audi car, supplied by the firm he works for, is usually parked in street in front of house.
